{
  "_comment": "Skeleton for the Greater meta-bot public seed bundle. The runtime loader fetches /seeds/greater.json (gitignored). Run `pnpm --filter @workspace/scripts run build-greater-seed` to generate the real bundle from the .pink properties + the public repo README. To extend the source list, append URLs in scripts/src/build-greater-seed.ts (SEED_URLS) or pass GREATER_EXTRA_URLS as a comma-separated env var.",
  "_private_overlay": "For operator-only notes that must not be committed (pricing for hire engagements, internal roadmap, app data not yet on the public web), hand-author a sibling file at artifacts/greater/public/seeds/greater-private.json with the same shape but `private: true` on each document. The runtime loader merges it on top of the public bundle, stamps each chunk with an internal:// page_url, and the citation UI renders those chunks as 'internal note' with no outbound link.",
